      "text": [
        "4169 - وَ فِي رِوَايَةِ حَرِيزٍ عَنْ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ مُسْلِمٍ عَنْ أَبِي جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ قَالَ : \"إِنْ خَرَجَ اَلدَّمُ فَكُلْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4169 - In the narration of Hariz from Muhammad ibn Muslim, from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), he said: \"If the blood flows, then eat.\""
        ]
      }
    }
